{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ciayo-games-hadiri-game-connection-america-2019/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CIAYO Games Hadiri Game Connection America 2019!","content":"\n<p>Hari ini menjadi hari yang spesial bagi CIAYO Games.\nPasalnya, CIAYO Games menjadi salah satu wakil Indonesia di acara Game\nConnection America 2019!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53336\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-hadiri-game-connection-america-2019/attachment/02-gca-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-gca-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Suasana meeting di Game Connection. Sumber: 80.lv\" class=\"wp-image-53336\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-gca-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Suasana meeting di Game Connection. Sumber: 80.lv</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai informasi, <a href=\"https://www.game-connection.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Game Connection (opens in a new tab)\">Game Connection</a> adalah sebuah event internasional dimana lebih dari 2700 pelaku industri video game; mulai dari developer, publisher, distributor, hingga pemilik platform bertemu untuk memamerkan game mereka dan mencari rekan kerja baru. Peserta yang hadir bukan nama-nama yang sembarangan. Ubisoft, Sega, Microsoft, EA, Playstation, Bandai Namco, hingga Activision merupakan beberapa pelaku industri besar yang hadir dalam Game Connection yang diadakan tak hanya di Amerika Serikat, namun juga di Eropa.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>CIAYO Games merupakan salah satu wakil dari Indonesia yang terbang ke San Francisco untuk menghadiri Game Connection America 2019. Bersama CIAYO Games ada Agate, MassHive Media, GameLevelOne, Semisoft, Wisageni Studio, Everidea Interactive, GameChanger Studio, Arsanesia, dan Megaxus Infotech. Hadirnya pelaku industri game Indonesia di acara ini adalah berkat usaha dari <a href=\"https://www.duniaku.net/2019/02/25/indonesia-game-connection-america-gca-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"BEKRAF dan AGI (opens in a new tab)\">BEKRAF dan AGI</a> untuk mendorong game Indonesia ke pasar Internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53337\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-hadiri-game-connection-america-2019/attachment/03-gca-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-gca-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Tim CIAYO Games. Sumber: CIAYO Games / Game Prime\" class=\"wp-image-53337\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-gca-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Tim CIAYO Games. Sumber: CIAYO Games / Game Prime</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>“Ini pertama kalinya kami berpartisipasi dalam Game\nConnection America,” ungkap Victorio Primadi, CEO CIAYO Corp. “Karena itu, kami\ningin membuka wawasan sekaligus mengenalkan produk dan IP CIAYO kepada pasar\ninternasional,” tambahnya. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tentunya, CIAYO Games bakal memperkenalkan berbagai game mereka di Game Connection America. Ada dua game yang diboyong ke negeri Paman Sam, yaitu CHIPS: Heroes Uprising dan CIAYO Stories.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"52371\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-chips-dan-straps/attachment/03-chips-x-straps/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-chips-x-straps\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-52371\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-chips-x-straps-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>CHIPS: Heroes Uprising. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>CHIPS: Heroes Uprising adalah game strategi mobile dengan berbagai fitur menarik seperti online raid, expedition, serta crafting. Dalam game ini CHIPS dan kawan-kawan harus bertahan hidup dengan mencegah serangan alien serta menyerang tower milik pemain lain. “Dalam acara ini, kami ingin memperluas jaringan serta mencari publisher global untuk CHIPS: Heroes Uprising,” jelas Victor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mentahkan Serangan Alien di Game CHIPS: Heroes Uprising!</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53177\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-dan-agate-luncurkan-game-dilan-official/attachment/04-game-dilan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-game-dilan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stories\" class=\"wp-image-53177\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/04-game-dilan-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Game official Dilan 1991. Sumber: CIAYO Stories</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sementara itu, CIAYO Stories adalah sebuah platform visual novel yang dikembangkan bersama Agate. Dalam CIAYO Stories, pemain bisa menjajal berbagai judul visual novel dengan berbagai macam cerita menarik. Salah satu judul yang bisa dimainkan dalam CIAYO Stories adalah game official Dilan 1991, yang diadaptasi dari novel, film, serta <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komik-dilan-1990-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"komik berjudul sama (opens in a new tab)\">komik berjudul sama</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/game-dilan-official-capai-ratusan-ribu-download/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Game Dilan Official Capai Ratusan Ribu Download</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53338\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-games-hadiri-game-connection-america-2019/attachment/04-gca-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-gca-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Oracle Park, salah satu venue Game Connection America 2019. Sumber: The San Francisco Examiner\" class=\"wp-image-53338\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-gca-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Oracle Park, salah satu venue Game Connection America 2019. Sumber: The San Francisco Examiner</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Game Connection America 2019 akan dilaksanakan sepanjang\nlima hari mulai dari tanggal 18 hingga 22 Maret 2019 di seluruh penjuru kota\nSan Francisco. Pada tanggal 18-19 Maret, para peserta akan memamerkan game\nmereka di Oracle Park, sementara tanggal 20-22 Maret para peserta bisa saling\nbertemu dan mengadakan meeting di berbagai lokasi di kota San Francisco. Good\nluck untuk CIAYO Games dan seluruh delegasi Indonesia di Game Connection\nAmerica 2019!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cd5e7a94-d53d-5f6b-a37e-d6b9fad01560"}}}